# FedLoad Project Rules

## Code Quality
- Follow PEP 8 and use type hints
- Document public functions and classes with docstrings
- Keep functions focused and small

## Testing
- Write unit and system tests for new features and bug fixes
- Use mocks for external dependencies in unit tests
- Mark tests (`unit`, `integration`, `system`, `security`)

## Security
- Validate and sanitize user and external inputs
- Secure password handling

## Documentation
- Document API endpoints, configuration options, usage examples
- Maintain changelog for releases and significant changes

## Configuration
- Use JSON files for configuration and persistent storage

## Deployment

- Use Docker for containerization and production deployment